This paper proposes a novel training methodology for improving the performance of Neural Ordinary Differential Equations (NODEs) in long-term time series forecasting. As such, it is likely to be relevant to several sub-categories of computer science, including machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural networks (cs.NE), signal processing (cs.SI), and computer vision (cs.CV).
